					<div>
						<p><lb/>Im <placeName ref="loc007683.02">bösen turn</placeName>
							<seg><lb/><origDate when="1623-03-27">27 <foreign xml:lang="la">martii</foreign> <hi rend="underline">1623</hi></origDate>, <foreign xml:lang="la"><choice><abbr>j</abbr><expan>judex</expan></choice></foreign> <persName><choice><abbr>Fleisch</abbr><expan><persName ref="per006840">Fleischman</persName></expan></choice></persName><note>Gemeint ist ein Stadtweibel.</note></seg>
							<seg><lb/><abbr>H</abbr> <persName ref="per006751">Erhart</persName>, <abbr>h</abbr> <persName ref="per009261">Techterman</persName></seg>
							<seg><lb/><persName ref="per009134">von Dießbach</persName>, <persName ref="per009455">Meister</persName>, <persName ref="per009451a.01"><choice><abbr>C</abbr> <expan>Christoph</expan></choice> von Ligertz</persName></seg>
							<seg><lb/><persName ref="per009485">Perroman</persName>, <persName ref="per009253">Bocard</persName>, <persName ref="per009460">Gottrow</persName></seg>
							<seg><lb/><choice><abbr>W</abbr> <expan>Weibel</expan></choice></seg></p>
						<p><seg><lb/><add place="left margin"><foreign xml:lang="la">Nihil <choice><abbr>ßt</abbr> <expan>solvit</expan></choice></foreign>.</add></seg>
							<seg><persName ref="per009534a.03">Pierre Feudi</persName> confirmant sa derniere <term ref="lem019465.01">confes<lb break="no"/>sion</term>, tant ses mesfaits de <term ref="lem018521">sorcellerie</term> que
								<lb/><term ref="lem019436.05">lareçains</term> commis, a sostenu n’avoir receu
								<lb/>la <term ref="lem018894.07">marque de <persName ref="per011219a.05">Sathan</persName></term>, mais d’avoir veu
								<lb/>en la <term ref="lem017043.01">secte</term> vers <placeName ref="loc007868.07">S<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Aubin</placeName> la <persName>Matysera</persName>
						<lb/><choice><abbr>als</abbr> <expan>alias</expan></choice> <persName>Belle Merciere</persName> <del>et German vendeur de
							<lb/><term ref="lem015448.02">curbiles</term></del>, <sic>barbe courte et meslée</sic>.<note>Le greffier aurait aussi dû biffer la description du dénommé German.</note></seg></p>
						<p><lb/>Item d’avoir employé la <term ref="lem018382.02">graise</term> receu de
							<lb/>son <term ref="lem019555.05">maistre</term> aux gens et bestes prememorés,
						<lb/>ne sachant touttefois s’ilz en son tous
						<lb/>morts&#160;; portant son intention estoit les
						<lb/>faire mourrir.</p>
						<p><lb/>A <placeName ref="loc008077.01">Kriegstetten</placeName> d’avoir emblé un pain, a
						<lb/><placeName ref="loc008084.02">Grange</placeName> riere <placeName ref="loc000738.09">Saleure</placeName> un pain.</p>
						<p><lb/>A <placeName ref="loc007597.02">Dirlaret</placeName> s’est aydé <term ref="lem015015.10">derober</term> un pain et di<lb break="no"/>mie un <term ref="lem018643.02">formage</term>.</p>
						<p><lb/>Au curial <persName>Charrey</persName> de <placeName ref="loc007682.03">Grandwillard</placeName> 3 <term ref="lem015449.02">gatte<lb break="no"/>lets</term>.</p>
						<p><lb/>En l’asle d’icy un pain d’un batz.</p>
						<p><lb/>A <placeName ref="loc008025.02">Corbaz</placeName> un pain.</p>
						<p><lb/>Et en tout encoures 4 fer de <term ref="lem018921.04">chevals</term>.</p>
						<p><lb/>Lesquels mesfaits a confirmé en la <term ref="lem019428.01">torture</term>,
							<lb/>priant les luy pardonner et faire <term ref="lem019504.02">grace</term>.<note>Der nächste Abschnitt betrifft das Verhör von <persName ref="per009535">François Feudy</persName>. Vgl. <ref target="urn:ssrq:SSRQ-FR-I_2_8-56.31-1">SSRQ FR I/2/8 56.31-1</ref>.</note></p>
						<p><lb/><add place="left margin">Hingricht mit <lb/>dem <term ref="lem007052.03">schwerdt</term>, <lb/><date when="1623-04-01">1<hi rend="sup"><unclear>ter</unclear></hi><foreign xml:lang="la">aprilis</foreign></date></add>.<note>Diese nachträgliche Marginalie steht im Original zu Beginn des Verhörs.</note></p>
